    "section_rich_text_gi3fgG": {
      "type": "section-rich-text",
      "name": "Rich text",
      "settings": {
        "section_title": "Top-quality Playground One Playset",
        "text": "<p>In a world of smartphones and games consoles, there’s nothing better than looking out the window to see your children playing on a high-quality wooden playset. Playground One is a leading provider of such sets, and we’re proud to supply and install Playground One playsets at Fenceworks. </p>",
        "section_width": "tiny",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 0,
        "section_bottom_margin": false
      }
    },
    "section_image_with_text_pR9LqQ": {
      "type": "section-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "image_rAdkNT": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/playground_installation_and_repair.png",
            "video": "",
            "video_button_color": "primary",
            "title": "Benefits of Choosing Playground One for Outdoor Playsets",
            "desc": "<p>Here are just some of the reasons to choose Playground One swing sets and other equipment:</p><h3>Pacific Solid Cedar</h3><p>At <a href=\"https://theguyon41.com/\" title=\"https://theguyon41.com/\">Fenceworks</a>, we align ourselves with premium products, and material underpins everything. Playground One sets use Pacific solid cedar, so you can be sure of durability through the seasons. </p><h3>Strong and Durable Design</h3><p>Features that bolster the strength of these playsets include tire chain connector cones, interlocking multi-beam joint construction, and oxidized hot dipped galvanized hardware. Your kids can love their playsets in the future just as much as they do now. </p><h3>Safety for Children </h3><p>Playground One has a reputation for considering its users, and this is evident with pinch-free safety swings, recessed nuts and bolts, snag-free safety hardware, and double wall safety slides. With all these features and more, you can be sure your children are safe while also having a great time. <br/></p>",
            "horizontal_align": "left",
            "link_title": "",
            "link": "",
            "bg_color_block": "#f2f2f2",
            "bg_color_content": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "color_text": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "text_heading_color": true,
            "text_border_color": true
          }
        },
        "image_GxFkDM": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/KC-1_Clubhouse.webp",
            "video": "",
            "video_button_color": "primary",
            "title": "Choosing the Right Playset for Your Home or Business",
            "desc": "<p>With various options, you may wonder how to choose a Playground One set. Here are some things to keep in mind:</p><h3>Available Space and Location </h3><p>Where do you plan to put the set, and how much space do you have in this location? A member of our friendly team can visit your property if you need help.</p><h3>Features </h3><p>What features will your children enjoy? Swings, climbing rope, slide, climbing wall, and more? From the Supreme Fort Combo 2 to the Turbo Deluxe Fort Combo 3, you have many options when it comes to Playground One playsets.</p><h3>Budget </h3><p>Feel free to browse the Playground One collection on this page - you’ll see that the prices vary depending on the set. If you have a specific budget in mind, allow our family to help you find the right set. <br/></p>",
            "horizontal_align": "left",
            "link_title": "Learn more",
            "link": "",
            "bg_color_block": "#e5e5e5",
            "bg_color_content": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "color_text": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "text_heading_color": true,
            "text_border_color": true
