    "section_testimonials_iTdP8a": {
      "type": "section-testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "text_aLharQ": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Jake at Fenceworks made this whole experience so perfect! My 18 month old twins are obsessed with the playground in our backyard! It is the best quality and will last for years and years to come!</p>",
            "name": "Jenna Zukin",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_RFaJBG": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Amazing family owned company, only place I refer my clients for fences, playgrounds and basketball hoops. Highly recommend going local with Fenceworks “The Guy on 41”!<br/></p>",
            "name": "Alec Mancheski",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_nkW9x7": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>They did an amazing job designing and installing my new playground swingset for my grandchildren, and met my deadline. Easy to work with, professional. Highly recommended!</p>",
            "name": "Debbie Eisenstein",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_QMAUMF": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Fenceworks is a fantastic family business that has been doing things the right way for decades. Their professionalism, customer service, and commitment to quality truly stand out. Highly recommend for any fencing or playground needs!</p>",
            "name": "Jon Escobar",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_f4hnNK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>They did an amazing job designing and installing my new playground swingset for my grandchildren, and met my deadline. Easy to work with, professional. Highly recommended!</p>",
            "name": "Debbie Eisenstein",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_cV9aRx": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>When it comes to a Fence instillation.. there is no better company in the north shore/chicago that I would recommend more than Fenceworks. They truly care about each customer like their family. I was informed every step of the way, true transparency throughout. Pricing was fair and competitive, and the craftsmanship was truly amazing. I look forward to buying a playground, trampoline, and basketball hoop this spring to wrap up all my home improvement projects in the future!<br/></p>",
            "name": "Adrish Saha",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_NBpWhf": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>I really can't say enough great things about Fenceworks! They always treat you with respect, honesty, and transparency. Regarding your next Fence project, look no further than \"The Guy on 41\"! I will be back this spring for Basketball Hoops, Trampolines, and Playgrounds... excited to complete my backyard with Fenceworks running the show!<br/></p>",
            "name": "J Cov",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        },
        "text_mb4EBE": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "media": "stars-brand",
            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>Jake at Fenceworks was excellent to work with. We are thrilled with our Playground One swingset that we got from them.</p>",
            "name": "Joe Janas",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
          }
        }
      },
